Files content and chronological order
-------------------------------------
Edite October 17, 2016


 1) interpolate_population.R   
    Create layers of population (5Km) 2001-2004, 2006-2009, 2011-2014 by interpolating
    the available data 2000, 2005, 2010, 2015
    Generates file: code_output/Population/GPW4_year.tif
    
 2) country_stats.R 
    Compute electricity access (delete: and households size per country)
    Generates file: code_output/country_stats.RData
    
 3) beta_regression.stan#vector_gp_mixed_noise.stan    
    Beta regression with GP #Multiple output GP with mixed Binomial and Gaussian likelihoods
 
 4) country_estimates_gp #vector_gp_interpolation.R    
    Calls beta_regression.stan #Calls vector_gp_mixed_noise.stan and generates samples form the process
    Generates file: code_output/country_annual_estimates.RData # code_output/vgpm_samples.RData

## 5) household_rasters.R   
##  Create layers of number of households (5Km) 2001-2015.
    Divide pixel-population by average number of household members per country.
    Generates files: code_output/Households/HHW4_year.tif
    
 6) z_covariates.R   
    Create layers of standardized covariates for the geostatistical model.
    Generates files: code_output/z_covariates/zpositive_ntl_year.tif
                     code_output/z_covariates/zpositive_pop_year.tif
                     code_output/z_covariates/zzero_pop_year.tif
    
 7) logit_r_offsets    
    Create rasters of linear predictor offsets
    
    
 8) dhs_preprocess.R
    Clean DHS surveys and organize them in a data frame
    
 9) additional_surveys_preprocess.R
    Put surveys, appart form DHS, in a data frame
    
10) third_set_surveys.R
    Put third set of surveys in a data frame
    
#10) dhs_w_covariates.R
#    Add covariates to data frame with DHS data
    
#11) other_data_w_covariates.R
#    Add covariates to data frame with additional surveys
    
#12) set3_w_covariates.R
#    Add covariates to set3
    
11) combine_datasets.R
    Merge DHS surveys and set 3
    
12) inla_preliminaries.R
    Define mesh and data indices
  
13) inla_model_w_offsets.R
    Code for running INLA
    
16) fig_validation.R //inla_model_validation.R
    ROC curves, and confusion matrices for test data
    
17) inla_model_interpolation_check.R
    Check the posterior approximation based on the interpolation of the latent field
    
18) inla_model_rasters.R
    Raster file of predicted probability of electricity
    
19) inla_model_country_aggregates.R
    Aggregated data per country
    
20) inla_model_ggplots.R
    gplots based on the raster files
    
    
..) fig_data.R
    Figure of data sources per country/year
    
..) fig_drivers.R
    Comparison between electricity access, lit pixels and light per Km^2
    
..) fig_zntl.R
    Comparison between electricity access offsets around the country average and zntl and zhouse
    
..) fig_posterior.R
    Prior and posterior distribution of Multioutput GP hyperparameters
    
..) fig_gpfit.R
    GP estimates of electricity access
    
..) fig_consistency    
    
..) tab_countries    
    
